{"tid":2423428,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為香港發聲！年輕時曾居於香港的日本人 飯野千春演奏「願榮光歸香港」","createTime":"2021-02-26T02:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T09:23:13.000Z","uid":192075,"like":142,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"09c0a60f7a5342cf50b8ddab085c8a20996ba3f0","tid":2423428,"uid":192075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:02:27.000Z","msg":"日前，西日本新聞報導，一名年輕時曾經在香港居住的日本人，飯野千春因為希望為中國控制日趨強硬而受苦的香港人打氣，在YouTube上公開了他用小號演奏了「願榮光歸香港」。他認為香港已經失去了當年自由的環境，因此希望為遇上困境的人們出一分力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/usapepe/status/1364419671018020864?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1364419671018020864%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_c10&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2Fino-chiharu-hk-song%2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fusapepe%2Fstatus%2F1364419671018020864%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1364419671018020864%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_c10%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.likejapan.com%252Flife%252Fino-chiharu-hk-song%252F&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=396e1b62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fusapepe%2Fstatus%2F1364419671018020864%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1364419671018020864%257Ctwgr%255E%257Ctwcon%255Es1_c10%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.likejapan.com%252Flife%252Fino-chiharu-hk-song%252F&h=c5254c4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/usapepe/status/1364419671018020864?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1364419671018020864%7Ctwgr%5E%7Ctwcon%5Es1_c10&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2Fino-chiharu-hk-song%2F</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\"><span class=\"x-large\"> 80年代曾居港 為香港的年輕人受苦感痛心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n飯野先生在1983年，25歲時因為公司研修來港居住一年。他回憶起當時的經歷，他仍然記得香港的同行面對重要的客戶仍然不會顧忌，隨心發言，這對常常要考慮對方心情的日本人十分特別，他對當時自由而雜亂的香港的所有東西都感到別具魅力。<br />\n<br />\n35年過去了，香港國安法在去年6月實施後，他再也感受不到這份曾經在香港存在的自由，並對新聞上見到警察把市民壓在地面，年輕人飽受催淚彈和水炮車的攻擊感到十分心痛。<br />\n<br />\n飯野先生在51歲時辭職入讀音樂短期大學，主修小號。在福岡創辦非牟利組織，在護老院舉辦了約300場的演奏會。去年12月，他以香港社運人士周庭被判刊為契機，思考自己能夠幫上甚麼忙，並構思上載影片。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nSBjUnOHqpk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnSBjUnOHqpk&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=d9f5989b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nSBjUnOHqpk</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\"><span class=\"x-large\"> 朋友因涉及政治拒絕幫忙 飯野先生獨自編曲演奏上載YouTube</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「願榮光歸香港」一曲廣為香港人認識，但被香港政府因「含強烈的政治訊息」視作嚴重問題。在國安法實施後，基本上不能唱了。<br />\n<br />\n飯野先生自己編曲，以小號等樂器演奏，最終製成約4分鐘的影片。影片中的鋼琴伴奏由朋友富永真由美幫忙，但有約10名朋友因不想參與政治活動而拒絕。飯野先生也明言擔心被中國盯上。自由表達言論的空間還存在嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/life/ino-chiharu-hk-song/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2Fino-chiharu-hk-song%2F&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6xhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=83630a8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/life/ino-chiharu-hk-song/</a>"},{"pid":"01ea537abd49462cb790af005b4ff11c8256971c","tid":2423428,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df37508eb33603e4b7dc84d86707246e9a0a0f2","tid":2423428,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eeea4b61715a24e22edc94da85db86eeb44ab07","tid":2423428,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T02:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 